 * [[http://링크 http://...이미지URL]]
 * [http://moniwiki.kldp.net/ http://moniwiki.kldp.net/imgs/moniwiki-logo.gif]
}}}
 * [http://moniwiki.kldp.net/ http://moniwiki.kldp.net/imgs/moniwiki-logo.gif]
----
<!> 두개의 대괄호로 하는 경우 (모니위키 1.1.5 이후)
{{{
 * [[http://링크 http://...이미지URL]]
 * [[http://moniwiki.kldp.net/ http://moniwiki.kldp.net/imgs/moniwiki-logo.gif]]
}}}
 * [[http://moniwiki.kldp.net/ http://moniwiki.kldp.net/imgs/moniwiki-logo.gif]]
----
{{{
 * [[wiki:페이지이름 http://...이미지URL]]
 * [[wiki:FrontPage http://moniwiki.kldp.net/imgs/moniwiki-logo.gif]]
}}}

 * [[wiki:FrontPage http://moniwiki.kldp.net/imgs/moniwiki-logo.gif]]
----
